trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of all [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elements in a project.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en samling av alla [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element i ett projekt.

trans-unit.source: Adds a new [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element to the end of the project.
trans-unit.target: Lägger till en ny [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element i slutet av projektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the new <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""> </xref> attribut för den nya <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""> </xref> element.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> object representing the created `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> objekt som representerar den skapade `Target` element.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> to a compatible one-dimensional <xref:System.Array>, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Kopierar hela <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref> till en kompatibel endimensionell <xref:System.Array>, från och med det angivna indexet för Målmatrisen.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> that is the destination of the elements copied from <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den endimensionell <xref:System.Array>som är mål för de element som kopieras från <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Array> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array>måste ha Nollbaserad indexering.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Det nollbaserade indexet i `array` vilka kopiera börjar.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the number of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> objects in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger antalet <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> objekt i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object in the collection represents a element in the project.
trans-unit.target: Varje <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>objekt i samlingen motsvarar ett element i projektet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>

trans-unit.source: An integer value representing the number of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Ett heltalsvärde som representerar antalet <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> objekt i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> exists in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Avgör om den angivna <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> finns i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the Target element to search for.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""> </xref> attribut för målelement att söka efter.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the `Target` element exists; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om den `Target` element finns, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en uppräknare går igenom den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden kan anroparen att använda den `foreach` instruktionen för C#-språk (`for each` i [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) att söka igenom enskilda <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>objekt i <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection> </xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> for the entire <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>för hela <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om åtkomst till den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref> är synkroniserade (trådsäkra).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om åtkomst till den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref> är synkroniserade (trådsäkra); i annat fall <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> object in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den angivna <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> objekt i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object represents a `Target` element in the project.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>objekt representerar en `Target` element i projektet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the Target element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""> </xref> attribut för mål-element i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The object that contains the property value specified by index.
trans-unit.target: Den objekt som innehåller den egenskapsvärde som anges av index .

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element from the project.
trans-unit.target: Tar bort angivna [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element från projektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element to remove.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""> </xref> attributet för den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""> </xref> element för att ta bort.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett objekt som kan användas för att synkronisera åtkomst till den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt som kan användas för att synkronisera åtkomst till den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.
